    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-ops SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-ops SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The ops team is responsible for the development and maintenance of OS system ops in openeuler community.。该 SIG 共有 68 名核心成员，维护 162 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler sig-ops SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler sig-ops SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/nvwa、src-openeuler/nvwa、openeuler/sysmonitor）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 ops@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-ops SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-ops SIG 共维护 162 个代码仓库，主要包括：openeuler/nvwa、src-openeuler/nvwa、openeuler/sysmonitor 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/sig-ops。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-ops SIG 的 Maintainer 是谁？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
